      <title>中国理想汽车降低汽车价格以争夺市场份额</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-li-auto-cuts-car-prices-market-share-battle-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国汽车制造商理想汽车周一将其五款车型中的四款降价约5%，并表示将向今年早些时候购买这些车型的车主退款，从而加深了中国的价格战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-li-auto-cuts-car-prices-market-share-battle-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 04:33:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
